It's a big enough difference that if I want to sell in Kelethin, I always sell at the Warrior's Guild -- I turned in enough shark meat there after three levels in the Queynos Sewers that I get better prices from the Emerald Warriors merchant than I do anywhere else. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ulunaltoadsnatcher.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lunal Toadsnatcher</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/15/02 1:29:11 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=19571.topic&index=54>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://home.earthlink.net/~bookfolk/_uimages/music4.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Grimling Gate rules</span><hr size=1> Faction is huge.  I get way better prices at ally than with warmly and I only have 60 charisma. <p><font face="Cornerstone"><font size=-1>Lunal Toadsnatcher</font></font><BR><font face="Cornerstone"><font size=-1><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=163741">Gnome Channeler of the Noble Cow (51)</a></font></font><BR><font face="Palacio"><font size=-1>Tholuxe Paells</font></font><BR><font size=-2><font face="Intrepid">Leader of </font><i><font face="Diploma"><a href="http://pub63.ezboard.com/btheelectoftholuxepaells">The Elect</a></font></i></font><BR><font face="Tahoma"><font size=-1>"<i>Nuke em from point blank range.  Its the only way to be sure</i>."</font></font></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/usnapdragyn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Snapdragyn</A></span><br>